slike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e573cb50980dbd37df8c5c0af2a1afb4d8be53e","tid":2100900,"uid":195796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"死法真係唔知想點<br />\n唔係有刀仔架咩<br />\n阿媽做咩落去玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f216cabbfe5c29deb0bfe9722f32d5aad83a23a3","tid":2100900,"uid":194370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"套野係真心差..."},{"pid":"6b9a02f919b40a3edc5b6e598820df66b3607b4f","tid":2100900,"uid":127469,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"成套基本上係冇反派<br />\n一開始睇覺得人設好怪，互助互愛到一個唔合理嘅地步<br />\n睇到最尾我先至明<br />\n我諗佢本身諗住食住奧運條水宣傳大和民旅精神<br />\n整體嚟講佢係日本嘅propaganda<br />\n<br />\n講返套動畫<br />\n可能我本身expect似望月峰太朗龍頭、又或者係原著日本沉沒咁<br />\n講人性殘酷、為生存不擇手段，就算mild極都有東京地震8.0咁<br />\n點知前完全講守望相助，所以個落差令我開頭嗰幾集好返感<br />\n<br />\n但係後半我真係有俾佢感動到<br />\n特別係師兄、Kite嗰兩段同個結尾"},{"pid":"94a72cc5324bd1ba108444dfaf955b23713eef54","tid":2100900,"uid":127469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7e573cb50980dbd37df8c5c0af2a1afb4d8be53e","tid":2100900,"uid":195796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"死法真係唔知想點<br />\n唔係有刀仔架咩<br />\n阿媽做咩落去玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"佢夾硬加咗句對白話冇刀仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗冇刀仔都仲有好多工具可以用<br />\n再唔係你喺架船到，大把野可以用嚟自製工具，佢地又唔係好趕時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada1190133e3baa873481c309ae1d2ca77287261","tid":2100900,"uid":48170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"有冇人反而覺得<br />\n係專登唔描述 究竟災難有幾慘烈<br />\n脫離災難嘅慘情 <br />\n對於唔同角色嘅離去 亦都冇太加以煽情<br />\n反而係淡淡一筆劃過<br />\n<br />\n有好多場面都有種荒謬而且違和嘅感覺<br />\n呢個我都唔係好get到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 睇過日本沉沒嘅漫畫版 初時仲以為佢呢套係另一個世界觀 點知原來田所 同小野寺都存在 不過新呢個小野寺咁老嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f825f2d3b6390d86449f6b318aed3bc7d6b2052","tid":2100900,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"如果可以長啲描述得仔細啲 可以做長篇動畫"},{"pid":"326994291dfdfdbc17e4106a8a7c1def8c628e82","tid":2100900,"uid":43369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾 可以唔洗晒時間"},{"pid":"8b8b384b72ac66a5356c833c5f96f91a57005f34","tid":2100900,"uid":151352,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T19:23:06.000Z","msg":"睇到第3集 <br />\n睇到r晒頭 硬係覺得成套野好有違和感<br />\n唔知想表達啲乜？<br />\n同埋個女好撚黑人憎 睇到反撚晒白眼<br />\n畫風都好唔掂"},{"pid":"34b84e3b511688640d1a41a34ff88c071da554fa","tid":2100900,"uid":194370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b8b384b72ac66a5356c833c5f96f91a57005f34","tid":2100900,"uid":151352,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T19:23:06.000Z","msg":"睇到第3集 <br />\n睇到r晒頭 硬係覺得成套野好有違和感<br />\n唔知想表達啲乜？<br />\n同埋個女好撚黑人憎 睇到反撚晒白眼<br />\n畫風都好唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T19:30:54.000Z","msg":"原著係一部好大日本主意同質疑外國嘅小説<br />\n用以前果套擺喺依套作品其實好夾硬<br />\n唔係日本人完全冇共嗚我諗應該好正常<br />\n呢套真係唔明點解可以做得咁差"},{"pid":"443ddcf34f16a73f610af18737a1488986c3a762","tid":2100900,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"10/10 ign"},{"pid":"d5c5452530f2f7c15748f8ae426550a3ceaa25ae","tid":2100900,"uid":194370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"443ddcf34f16a73f610af18737a1488986c3a762","tid":2100900,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"10/10 ign"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T19:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ee05bc47c7998e90327a46